<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l5"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt vns gerett . daʒ wır <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> verfolgt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gütlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l6">tag vor <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu <expan>ſuche<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu Sulcʒbach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l7">auf den ſunntag vor ſand Jacobs tag ſchıerıſt ʒu nacht da ʒu ſein . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l8">wir eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ . daʒ Jr vns einen auſʒ <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> reten auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l9"><expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag <expan>leıhe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ſenden wellet . der bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> da ſey vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_198_r2l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gelimpf vnd vngelimpf da <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höre</expan> . vnd getrawen <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> wol </ab>
